753
01:07:45,049 --> 01:07:50,487
Outstanding athlete in basketball, baseball,
football, always made the first team.

754
01:07:50,809 --> 01:07:55,280
He always played to win,
played hard, but clean.

755
01:07:58,649 --> 01:08:02,164
