838
01:16:21,289 --> 01:16:23,280
Kid, you're a positive genius.

839
01:16:23,369 --> 01:16:24,802
-Happy New Year!
-Likewise.

840
01:16:24,889 --> 01:16:26,766
Keep digging, old-timer.

841
01:16:46,569 --> 01:16:48,764
Never seen so much blonde chicken.

842
